{"tid":2037532,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"學生手持「光復香港，時代革命」旗幟　校長指不罰學生","createTime":"2020-05-27T04:51:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T05:12:12.000Z","uid":241764,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"783a1cc356b8fdf8a9529ca0f1f7393e165fb900","tid":2037532,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T04:51:15.000Z","msg":"中三至中五學生今日復課，網上有人號召罷課。在將軍澳的基督教宣道會宣基中學，有學生在校內向鏡頭舉起「五大訴求，缺一不可」的手勢。另外，在石峽尾的「廠商會中學」，有學生在操場手持「光復香港，時代革命」的旗幟。<br />\n<br />\n廠商會中學校長麥耀光表示，校方事前不知道學生有這個行動，認為學生可以表達訴求，該名學生其後已返回課室上堂，會安排老師及社工了解情況，協商要在上課及表達訴求中取平衡。<br />\n<br />\n他說，校方不會懲罰學生，認為懲罰可以即時停止學生的行為，但會令學生感到不快，不能解決問題，價值觀問題上應採取引導的教育方式，校方亦認為學生不應將政治帶入校園，會引導及教育學生，不擔心教育局因為事件向校方施壓。<br />\n<br />\n他提到，校方一直均有關心及跟進學生的情況，不會就事件特別向全校做廣播呼籲，相信校方能夠好好處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528613-20200527.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528613-20200527.htm&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8U9g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=caa7e1ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528613-20200527.htm&h=86dc7dd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528613-20200527.htm</a>"},{"pid":"38589fd6d293c8dd0ee92a9a90635f2fc2dbda95","tid":2037532,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T04:51:53.000Z","msg":"[文宣方向][跳出同溫層]民意調查分析<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2037458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2037458</a>"},{"pid":"d9563ad1e6d613d9668cf295241dc04d38c99a4d","tid":2037532,"uid":76341,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T04:53:06.000Z","msg":"應該全部同我罰抄100次貼壁報板呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8270b8775c552df6fbae3193494054988f271880","tid":2037532,"uid":28432,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T04:58:27.000Z","msg":"講野好得體 搵唔到位駁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca28c34bc753500422e90f6ee22c776fb73b6db3","tid":2037532,"uid":134474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:10:02.000Z","msg":"梓樂母校<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b980292f8e6466ed3243aed2483dc545e09481a3","tid":2037532,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72696b7d0746a69c038125dcc3171943ba5f073","tid":2037532,"uid":263618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca28c34bc753500422e90f6ee22c776fb73b6db3","tid":2037532,"uid":134474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:10:02.000Z","msg":"梓樂母校<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:11:20.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1e8b3d058c49e2f496d6b9956cb3a3633affe1","tid":2037532,"uid":351279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:12:12.000Z","msg":"學生不應把政治帶入校園, 港共就積極將政治滲透校園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}